('34045e5b-6633-81b1-8567-ddfbb3046fd8', 'Yenxa — Investor Match', 'Stalled', 'Investor Match', NULL, 'Not Scored', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Confirm Yenxa''s current runway status with Jose Manuel. If still active, introduce to at least one investor contact in CH network by end of April. Urgency: startup is post-zero-runway.', 'URGENT — Notes from Nov 2025 state runway = 0 months. Human has confirmed engagement is still active (founders contributing capital). Investor introduction is existential, not optional. Opportunity created 2026-04-12 by portfolio-health-agent execute run.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'None', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.notion.so/Yenxa-Investor-Match-34045e5b663381b18567ddfbb3046fd8', '2026-04-12T12:59:00.000Z', '2026-04-12T12:59:00.000Z', '2026-04-15T14:04:00.000Z'),
('34045e5b-6633-81b1-ae3f-f05024fca358', 'iRefill × UNDP — Investor Match', 'Stalled', 'Investor Match', NULL, 'Not Scored', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'UNDP is already funding the Auto Mercado Fase 2 pilot. Warm introduction path exists — leverage existing UNDP contact to explore expanded grant or programme funding for iRefill LATAM scale-up. Prioritize before Auto Mercado machine delivery (May 2026) to have pilot evidence in hand.', 'Match proposed by deal-flow-agent (investor-matchmaker) — Score: 68/90. Funder: UNDP (34045e5b-6633-81e6-b46e-fd7822cf4e5b). Signals fired: (1) Sector overlap — UNDP themes Climate/Zero Waste/Public Sector match iRefill Reuse/Refill/Retail/Climate category (+28); (2) Existing active relationship — UNDP is funding Year 1 software maintenance for the iRefill Auto Mercado Fase 2 pilot in Costa Rica (+15); (3) Stage signal — active funder already engaged at pilot stage (+15); (4) Startup type match — refill/circular/sustainability keywords in both records (+10). Run date: 2026-04-12. Confidence: Medium. This is a SPECIFIC funder record. The generic ''iRefill — Investor Match'' placeholder (34045e5b-6633-81e3-83fa-ed2d69f70f9c) remains open separately.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'None', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.notion.so/iRefill-UNDP-Investor-Match-34045e5b663381b1ae3ff05024fca358', '2026-04-12T13:13:00.000Z', '2026-04-12T13:13:00.000Z', '2026-04-15T14:04:00.000Z'),
('34045e5b-6633-81b4-a2f4-cf8204d025c6', 'Retail Refill Implementation — Tesco', 'Stalled', 'CH Sale', NULL, 'Below Threshold', 'P3 — Backlog', 'Low — <30%', NULL, NULL, 'Retail Refill Implementation offer cue — Tesco flagged as high-scale opportunity. Long decision cycle means early pipeline entry is critical.', NULL, NULL, 'Map Tesco sustainability and own-brand innovation contacts. Identify whether a regional or store-level entry point is more realistic than central procurement.', 'Sprint 24 Qualification Audit (2026-04-12): Score 43/100 — Below Threshold. No access path, no named contact, enterprise-scale mismatch. Created from Offer Cue only. Decision Item open recommending Closed Lost / Deprioritized. Return to Offer Cue in Retail Refill Active offer.', 'Tesco is the UK''s largest grocer with scale impact potential. They have a formal sustainability strategy (Little Helps Plan) and have trialled refill in select stores. A CH-managed pilot-to-programme model could support their sustainability team without requiring central procurement renegotiation. Value at scale is significant but decision cycle is long.', NULL, NULL, 'None', 43, 'Retail Refill Implementation offer cue — Tesco flagged as high-scale opportunity. Long decision cycle means early pipeline entry is critical.', 'https://www.notion.so/Retail-Refill-Implementation-Tesco-34045e5b663381b4a2f4cf8204d025c6', '2026-04-12T19:51:00.000Z', '2026-04-12T19:51:00.000Z', '2026-04-15T14:02:00.000Z'),
('34045e5b-6633-81b5-bbc9-f1bd949ea6d2', 'Retail Refill Implementation — Sainsbury''s', 'Stalled', 'CH Sale', NULL, 'Below Threshold', 'P3 — Backlog', 'Low — <30%', NULL, NULL, 'Retail Refill Implementation offer cue — Sainsbury''s flagged as P3 UK grocery target.', NULL, NULL, 'Research Sainsbury''s sustainability procurement and Future Brands contacts. Cross-reference with any existing CH network connections.', 'Sprint 24 Qualification Audit (2026-04-12): Score 42/100 — Below Threshold. No named contact, no access path, no buyer-side trigger. Created from Offer Cue. Decision Item open recommending Closed Lost / Deprioritized. Return to Offer Cue in Retail Refill Active offer.', 'Sainsbury''s has an active sustainability strategy (Sainsbury''s Future Brands and sustainability commitments) and has trialled refill formats in select stores. Their Taste the Difference and own-label ranges align with a premium refill positioning. Decision cycles are long but sustainability team is accessible.', NULL, NULL, 'None', 42, 'Retail Refill Implementation offer cue — Sainsbury''s flagged as P3 UK grocery target.', 'https://www.notion.so/Retail-Refill-Implementation-Sainsbury-s-34045e5b663381b5bbc9f1bd949ea6d2', '2026-04-12T19:51:00.000Z', '2026-04-12T19:51:00.000Z', '2026-04-15T14:02:00.000Z'),
('34045e5b-6633-81c6-a061-fbf4d7414e44', 'Fair4All Finance Scale-up — SUFI', 'Qualifying', 'Grant', NULL, 'Not Scored', 'P1 — Act Now', 'Medium — 30–70%', '34045e5b-6633-8122-a242-fef9dc9b2f55', 'Fair4All Finance', 'Scale-up programme window open (confirmed in Sprint 18 portfolio brief). P1 action already surfaced in Decision Center.', NULL, NULL, '1. Confirm SUFI eligibility criteria with Fair4All Finance directly. 2. Submit Expression of Interest. 3. Deadline: April 30, 2026.', NULL, 'SUFI''s financial inclusion mission directly aligns with Fair4All Finance mandate. Scale-up capital supports organizations providing affordable finance to people in vulnerable circumstances. 1.4m unbanked UK adults (FCA data) confirms market size.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Scale-up programme window open (confirmed in Sprint 18 portfolio brief). P1 action already surfaced in Decision Center.', 'https://www.notion.so/Fair4All-Finance-Scale-up-SUFI-34045e5b663381c6a061fbf4d7414e44', '2026-04-12T18:19:00.000Z', '2026-04-12T18:19:00.000Z', '2026-04-12T18:19:00.000Z'),
('34045e5b-6633-81e3-83fa-ed2d69f70f9c', 'iRefill — Investor Match', 'Stalled', 'Investor Match', NULL, 'Not Scored', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'iRefill has 5 active pilots, ARR $120K. Map impact investors (climate tech, consumer hardware, LATAM) who could support Series A preparation. Auto Mercado pilot results (June 2026) will be key evidence.', 'Seed stage, $120K ARR (Nov 2025), 8% equity held by CH. CH is well-positioned to make introductions via ZWF Forum / COP31 investor network. Opportunity created 2026-04-12.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'None', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.notion.so/iRefill-Investor-Match-34045e5b663381e383faed2d69f70f9c', '2026-04-12T12:59:00.000Z', '2026-04-12T12:59:00.000Z', '2026-04-15T14:05:00.000Z'),
('34045e5b-6633-81f3-9cf7-e5b383de69fc', 'IDB Lab Innovation Grant — SUFI / LATAM Financial Inclusion', 'Qualifying', 'Grant', NULL, 'Not Scored', 'P4 — Watch', NULL, '33f45e5b-6633-81b3-84ef-fa1ad08b091b', 'SUFI', 'Editado desde Grants Desk — 2026-04-13', NULL, NULL, 'Confirm SUFI LATAM entity or implementation partner status. Review IDB Lab open challenge windows. Assess whether SUFI stage and traction level meets IDB Lab minimum bar.', NULL, 'IDB Lab (IADB innovation lab) funds fintech and financial inclusion solutions in Latin America. SUFI''s unbanked market model is an exact fit by geography and theme. Grant access requires LATAM entity or strong LATAM implementation partner — CH needs to confirm SUFI''s regional entity status.', NULL, NULL, 'Needed', NULL, 'Editado desde Grants Desk — 2026-04-13', 'https://www.notion.so/IDB-Lab-Innovation-Grant-SUFI-LATAM-Financial-Inclusion-34045e5b663381f39cf7e5b383de69fc', '2026-04-12T18:24:00.000Z', '2026-04-12T18:24:00.000Z', '2026-04-13T21:41:00.000Z'),
('34045e5b-6633-81f9-8889-ca5f39544e96', 'Yenxa — CH Sale', 'Stalled', 'CH Sale', NULL, 'Not Scored', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Confirm Yenxa''s 3 active pilots are still live. Identify next CH-originated sales target for Yenxa oil-to-soap technology.', '15% rev share to CH. Product: IoT soap dispenser from used cooking oil. 3 active pilots. Revenue share engagement. Opportunity created 2026-04-12.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'None', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.notion.so/Yenxa-CH-Sale-34045e5b663381f98889ca5f39544e96', '2026-04-12T12:59:00.000Z', '2026-04-12T12:59:00.000Z', '2026-04-15T14:04:00.000Z'),
